r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">We recommended to form data into crypto-containers, and then transfer them to storage.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Incoming traffic on the server is not limited, the outgoing traffic must be less than 10% of the amount of the data stored per day.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">The access to the data is limited to 5 IP-addresses.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Your account is debited daily on the basis of calculation: (amount of stored data * </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">0.3 cents</span></span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">) / 30.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">The service is intended only for the storage of data for the purpose of backup.</span></span></p>',NULL,NULL),(54,117,'DNS hosting',1,NULL,NULL,'This service involves hosting of your DNS zones on our equipment. You have the ability to edit the contents of the zone and adjust the DNS settings of your domains.','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><strong>DNS hosting</strong></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">This service involves hosting of your DNS zones on our equipment. You have the ability to edit the contents of the zone and adjust the DNS settings of your domains.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">It is possible to configure up to 100 records.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Price: € 1 per month for 1 domain.</span></span></p>',NULL,NULL),(55,55,'HGJHFKHF',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0.00','56.00');

