hicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>Russia</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">DDoS protection service offered by HOSTKEY has been jointly implemented with our technology partners: network backbone operator RETN and Arbor Networks &mdash; global leader in network security solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px\">Service features</span></strong></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Protection against bulk Volumetric-attacks, all types of traffic are being filtered.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Connection to the service does not require a prolonged setup, software installation, etc. The server connects to a secure network and basic filters are turned on automatically.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">The possibility of &quot;additional training&quot; of the system. Within two weeks from the connection date, the system teaches itself by analyzing traffic types. Further, there will be a possibility of adjusting filtering rules.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Only cleaned incoming traffic is being charged.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">