ess indicated in the claim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any claims made by anonyms or delivered by e-mail or fax WILL NOT be accepted and considered.</p>','section/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/85/secure_mail.png'),(86,81,'/solutions/software-service','software-service',NULL,'Content_Page','Content_Section_Page','no','yes','yes','yes',30,'Software</br>as a</br>Service','Software','Wide selection of licensed software','Software-as-a-Service','Software-as-a-Service','Software-as-a-Service','<p><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Microsoft licenses are available via SPLA on monthly basis</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY provides Microsoft software licenses available <b><a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/Licensing/licensing-programs/spla-program.aspx\"><span style=\"color:#945AE0;\">via SPLA contract</span></a></b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Those licenses can only be used on HOSTKEY&rsquo;s servers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF692d;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>Windows Server</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"table_stan\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">License</span></span></strong></strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">VPS</span></span></strong></strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Monthly, &euro;</span></span></strong></strong></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-fami