nected to networks of such telecom operators as RETN, NETBYNET, etc. that have direct channels to CITY SYSTEMS, DATALINE and DATAPRO data centers. Networks of these operators are based on highly reliable telecommunication equipment and have multiple redundancy that provides network accessibility of server equipment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">Connection to the network of the international operator RETN makes it possible to provide services with high level of accessibility not only in the Russian Federation:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">The network uses Internet Exchange nodes in Europe, USA and Asia, and it is constantly growing.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color: rgb(255, 105, 45);\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">It is capable of maintaining 100G channels, with a total of 7.2Tbit/s per fiber pair.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF692d;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicmedicondosc\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>The Netherlands</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">HOSTKEY has a reserved connection to Serverius, RETN networks and several traffic exchange points, in particular AMS-IX:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Serverius network provides a mix of huge amount of peering and ip-transit providers: AMS-IX, DE-CIX, GTT&nbsp;Tinet, Level3, DE-CIX, TATA communications, NL-IX, RETN and many other partial and full transit and private fiber peers.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Each peering or carrier is connected to multiple 10G ports and is part of the 300Gbps network that is running on our redundant 400Gbps transport backbone to multiple Amsterdam and Frankfurt data centers. Route preferences are not specified, so you always get the shortest routes to other networks.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\">It allows us to provide our clients with multiple ports, thus ensuring a complete redundancy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:franklingothicbookcondc;\"><a href=\"/support/speedtest/\"><span style=\"color:#945AE0;\"><b>Test</b></span></a> your Internet connection speed to our locations in Russia and The Netherlands.</span></span></p>','section/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/100/96/network.png'),(97,76,'/about/datacenter','datacenter',NULL,'Content_Page','Content_Section_Page','no','yes','yes','yes',40,'<span class=\"White-header\">Data centers</span>','Data centers','Data centers',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h2>Our data centers span over</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tab_block\">\r\n<div class=\"tabs\"><a class=\"tab1 tab_sel\" href=\"#\">data center comparison</a> <a class=\"tab2\" href=\"#\">City Systems</a> <a class=\"tab3\" href=\"#\">DataLine</a> <a class=\"tab4\" href=\"#\">DataPro</a> <a class=\"tab5\" href=\"#\">Serverius</a>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tab_html\">\r\n<div class=\"html_tab html_tab1\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Location</strong></td>\r\n			<td align=\"center\"><b>MOSCOW</b><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			City Systems <img src=\"/assets/img/city_logo.png\" /></td>\r\n			<td align=\"center\"><b>MOSCOW</b><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			DataLine <img src=\"/assets/img/dataline_logo.png\" /></td>\r\n			<td align=\"center\"><b>MOSCOW</b><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			DataPro <img src=\"/assets/img/Datapro_400.png\" /></td>\r\n			<td align=\"center\"><b>DRONTEN</b><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			Serverius <img src=\"/assets/img/Serverius.png\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>TIER level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>TIER II uncertified</td>\r\n			<td><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/dtln_tier.png\" style=\"width: 32px;\" />TIER III certified</td>\r\n			<td><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro1.png\" style=\"width: 32px;\" /><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro2.png\" style=\"width: 32px;\" /><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro3.png\" style=\"width: 32px;\" /><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			TIER III certified</td>\r\n			<td>TIER III uncertified</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Units per &ldquo;19 rack</strong></td>\r\n			<td>47</td>\r\n			<td>42</td>\r\n			<td>42</td>\r\n			<td>45</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Power per rack, up to</strong></td>\r\n			<td>20 KWh</td>\r\n			<td>10 KWh</td>\r\n			<td>28 KWh</td>\r\n			<td>7,5 KWh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Cages and customized racks available</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Security certification level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&mdash;</td>\r\n			<td>ISO/IEC 27001:2013<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			PCI Data Security 3.0</td>\r\n			<td>PCI Data Security 3.1</td>\r\n			<td>ISO/IEC 27001:2013<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			ISO 9001:2008</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Authorized access and support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"html_tab html_tab2\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h2>City Systems</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/assets/img/CitySystems-big.jpg\" />\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>location</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Moscow</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>TIER level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>TIER II uncertified</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Units per &ldquo;19 rack</strong></td>\r\n			<td>42</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Power per rack,<br />\r\n			up to</strong></td>\r\n			<td>20 KWh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Cages and customized racks available</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Security certification level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&mdash;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Authorized access and support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>City Systems data center was built in accordance with TIER II standards. It is located in a close proximity to Moscow city center. The data center is equipped with:</p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Two independent power supply systems.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Each system has the capacity of 1 MW.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">1250 kVA diesel generator set (DGS) operating in automatic mode.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Three uninterruptible power supply units (UPS) operating under N+1 scheme.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">300 kVA each, excess air conditioning and air humidifying systems.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Automatic fire extinguishing systems.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Security systems for perimeter protection and unauthorized access prevention.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Including video surveillance system.</span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"html_tab html_tab3\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h2>DataLine</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/assets/img/DataLine-big.jpg\" />\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>location</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Moscow</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>TIER level</strong></td>\r\n			<td><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/dtln_tier.png\" style=\"width: 50px;\" /><br />\r\n			TIER III certified</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Units per &ldquo;19 rack</strong></td>\r\n			<td>42</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Power per rack,<br />\r\n			up to</strong></td>\r\n			<td>10 KWh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Cages and customized racks available</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Security certification level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>ISO/IEC 27001:2013<br />\r\n			PCI Data Security 3.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Authorized access and support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Data center Dataline Nord was built in 2007 and is now offering its customers a possibility of placing equipment in a data center that has the following characteristics:</p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Total area of 10,684 square meters.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Total power capacity of 18200 KW.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Power per rack: 6 kW or higher.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">10 server rooms.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">1712 commercial racks.</span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n\r\n			<p>Multi-level infrastructure of this data center includes gas extinguishing systems, CCTV and alarm monitoring system as well as access control. Power supply including backup is structured in accordance with 2N scheme. Power to each rack is supplied via 2 rays. Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) is located inside the data center modules. Backup diesel generator sets are setup according to N+1 scheme: two generators are sufficient to provide power supply to a data center plus one backup one in case of emergency.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"html_tab html_tab4\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h2>DataPro</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/assets/img/DataPro-big.jpg\" />\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>location</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Moscow</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>TIER level</strong></td>\r\n			<td><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro1.png\" style=\"width: 50px;\" /><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro2.png\" style=\"width: 50px;\" /><img class=\"cert\" src=\"/upload/data_content/data_pro3.png\" style=\"width: 50px;\" /><br />\r\n			TIER III certified</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Units per &ldquo;19 rack</strong></td>\r\n			<td>42</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Power per rack,<br />\r\n			up to</strong></td>\r\n			<td>28 KWh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Cages and customized racks available</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Security certification level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>PCI Data Security 3.1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Authorized access and support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>DataPro data center in Moscow was commissioned in December 2014 and is by far the largest of the stated objects of its kind in Russia and Eastern Europe with:</p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Total area of 16,000 sq.m.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Total power supply of 25 MW.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Capability of accommodating up to 3,000 racks of IT equipment.</span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n\r\n			<p>Design and construction of this data center was carried out in accordance with international best practices and to the highest international standards.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>DataPro has received TIER III Uptime Institute Certification. It is one of the most technologically advanced and energy efficient commercial data centers in Russia.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"html_tab html_tab5\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<h2>Serverius</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/upload/data_content/Serverius.png\" />\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>location</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Dronten</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>TIER level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Tier III uncertified</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Units per &ldquo;19 rack</strong></td>\r\n			<td>45</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Power per rack,<br />\r\n			up to</strong></td>\r\n			<td>7,5 KWh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Cages and customized racks available</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Security certification level</strong></td>\r\n			<td>ISO/IEC 27001:2013<br />\r\n			ISO 9001:2008</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Authorized access and support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>The Serverius DC is a carrier-neutral Tier III data center located in-between the world&rsquo;s largest internet backbones of Amsterdam and Frankfurt. This data center uses the most modern technology; it is completely CO2 neutral and runs on 100% green energy. Due to &ldquo;Cold Corridor System&rdquo; the data center is highly energy efficient. The entire grounds are fenced, the DC is equipped with CCTV (both inside and outside), &ldquo;Smart Cards&rdquo; are used for enhanced security.</p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Total amount of racks: 200.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Power per rack: 32A.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Racks, 1000mm deep and 45U high (almost 10% higher than normal racks).</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Redundant N+1 cooling (1.3 EUE).</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Redundant N+1 power supplies (incl. generator set).</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Redundant N+1 UPS.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Diesel storage tanks that are able to run for 24 hours without external power.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Certified fire detection and prevention installation.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">VESDA.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#FF692d\"><span style=\"color:rgb(39, 46,56);\">Data center connected to the 10kV ring to ensure power.</span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b-text-page__box .tab_block {\r\n    margin: 0 auto 30px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n}\r\n.b-text-page__box .tabs a.tab1 {\r\n    width: 160px;\r\n}\r\n.b-text-page__box .tabs a.tab2 {\r\n    width: 125px;\r\n    padding-left: 40px;\r\n    background-image: url(/assets/img/ru_flag.png);\r\n    backgro